# Conda Environment Rule

description: This project uses conda base environment as the default Python environment
alwaysApply: true

---

- Use conda base environment for all Python operations
- Python interpreter path: /opt/conda/bin/python
- Conda path: /opt/conda/bin/conda
- All terminal operations should activate conda base environment
- Use `conda activate base` when starting new terminal sessions
